== Wiki-product

A flexible database to describe products
Model: describe a hierarchical set of features (boolean, numeric, enumerated, text, etc...). You can see that as form.
Product: each product is described by a set of model. For each model, the product is described by a set of feature values. 
Doesn't cover the rating

- design for crowd sourcing and aggregation
- provide: product search and product similarities
- API for external use

